| Field             | Type   | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
+-------------------+--------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| stddev(f)         | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| stddev(d)         | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| stddev(f_10_2)    | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| stddev(d_12_3)    | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| stddev(f_60_10)   | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| stddev(d_60_11)   | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| stddev(f_255_30)  | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| stddev(d_255_30)  | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| stddev(dec_15_3)  | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| stddev(dec_40_30) | double | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
+-------------------+--------+------+-----+---------+-------+
drop table td;

drop table t1;
drop database mysql_double_md;
